          <h3>üìà Growth Potential</h3>
          <p>With incoming investments and infrastructure projects, the Sunshine Coast is a hotbed for sustainable property growth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>üë®‚Äçüë©‚Äçüëß‚Äçüë¶ Family-Friendly</h3>
          <p>Top-rated schools, parks, and community-focused living make this the perfect place to raise a family.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>üèñÔ∏è Beachside Living</h3>
          <p>From Mooloolaba's relaxed charm to Maroochydore's dynamic community, find your perfect coastal lifestyle.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Preview Section -->
  <section class="about-preview">
    <div class="container about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>About Jack McGhee</h2>
        <p>
          I'm Jack McGhee, a senior real estate professional with over 20 years of experience 
          delivering premium results in Australia's most competitive property markets.
        </p>
