          After relocating to the Sunshine Coast with my young family, I'm now proud to call 
          Mooloolaba home and bring metropolitan expertise to a community I've long admired.
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary">Read My Story</a>
      </div>
      <div class="about-image">
        <div class="image-placeholder">
          <span>Jack McGhee</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Recent Blog Posts -->
  <section class="blog-preview">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Latest Insights</h2>
      <div class="blog-grid">
        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <span class="blog-date">December 2025</span>
            <h3>The Sunshine Coast Property Market: 2026 Outlook</h3>
            <p>Discover the trends shaping the Sunshine Coast real estate market and what they mean for buyers and sellers...</p>
            <a href="/blog/sunshine-coast-market-outlook-2026" class="blog-link">Read More ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <span class="blog-date">November 2025</span>
            <h3>5 Tips for First-Time Home Buyers</h3>
            <p>Navigating your first property purchase can be overwhelming. Here's my expert advice to make it seamless...</p>
            <a href="/blog/first-time-buyer-tips" class="blog-link">Read More ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
        <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-secondary">View All Articles</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* Hero Section */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-deep) 0%, var(--ocean-blue) 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
      margin-top: -1px;
    }

    .hero-content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .hero-text {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .hero-title .accent {
      color: var(--gold-light);
      display: block;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--sand-warm);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--gold-accent);
      color: var(--ocean-deep);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--gold-light);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.4);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--white);
      border: 2px solid var(--white);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--ocean-deep);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .stat {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--sand-warm);
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* Services Section */
    .services {
      padding: 6rem 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--ocean-deep);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .service-card {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .service-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .service-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .service-card h3 {
      color: var(--ocean-deep);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .service-card p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .service-link {
      color: var(--ocean-blue);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .service-link:hover {
      color: var(--gold-accent);
    }

    /* Why Sunshine Coast */
    .why-sunshine-coast {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      background: var(--sand-warm);
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .feature {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--gold-accent);
    }

    .feature h3 {
      color: var(--ocean-deep);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .feature p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* About Preview */
    .about-preview {
      padding: 6rem 0;
    }

    .about-content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-text h2 {
      color: var(--ocean-deep);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-text p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .about-text .btn {
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .image-placeholder {
      aspect-ratio: 4/5;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-blue) 0%, var(--ocean-light) 100%);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
    }

    /* Blog Preview */
    .blog-preview {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      background: var(--sand-light);
    }

    .blog-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .blog-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .blog-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .blog-image-placeholder {
      height: 200px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-light) 0%, var(--sand-warm) 100%);
    }

    .blog-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .blog-date {
      color: var(--gold-accent);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .blog-card h3 {
      color: var(--ocean-deep);
      margin: 0.75rem 0;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .blog-card p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .blog-link {
      color: var(--ocean-blue);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .blog-link:hover {
      color: var(--gold-accent);
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }

      .hero-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .about-content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .services-grid,
      .features-grid,
      .blog-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
